    "testimonials_mUYTyV": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_wMckqe": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Heybike Ranger S is a killer city cruiser with one unfortunate quirk. Heybike continues to produce quality e-bikes, and this one really packs a punch.</p>",
            "author": "CNET",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/CNET.png",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "scribble",
            "highlighted_scribble": "squiggle-underline"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_mJQm9n": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Mars 2.0: Solidly built and fun to ride. It’s indeed a capable commuter for city dwellers and van lifers.</p>",
            "author": "Tom's Guide",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Tom_s_Guide.png",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "scribble",
            "highlighted_scribble": "squiggle-underline"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_CUtjf9": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Mars 2.0 is an affordable multi-purpose folding bike with a smooth ride and fast speed!  </p>",
            "author": "Electricbike Report",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Electricbike_report.png",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "scribble",
            "highlighted_scribble": "squiggle-underline"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_h3VVAf": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Horizon is more than just a pretty paint job. It is a versatile ebike with beautiful red, orange, and yellow colors. It stands out among all the ebikes on the market.</p>",
            "author": "Eletreck",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Eletreck.png",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "scribble",
            "highlighted_scribble": "squiggle-underline"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_NkxBAM": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Heybike Horizon comes fully loaded with front and rear suspension, wide 4.0” tires, and the ability to collapse down during storage or transport.</p>",
            "author": "Mounatin Weekly News",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Mounatin_Weekly_News.png",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_ArgjGU": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Heybike Tyson Review: This comfortable fat-tire ebike is an affordable way to dip your toes into the electric bike lifestyle, without breaking the bank.</p>",
            "author": "WIRED",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/WIRED.png",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
